凯文·史密斯记得莎南·多赫蒂制作《Mallrats 2》的最后请求https://www.nme.com/news/film/kevin-smith-remembers-shannen-dohertys-final-request-to-make-mallrats-2-3778924?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=kevin-smith-remembers- Shannen-Dohertys-制作 Mallrats-2 的最终请求Sam WarnerMon, 29 Jul 2024 16:01:02 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3778924 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kevin-Smith-and-Shannen-Doherty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="凯文·史密斯和莎南·多尔蒂" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kevin-Smith-and-Shannen-Doherty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kevin-Smith-and-Shannen-Doherty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kevin-Smith-and-Shannen-Doherty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kevin-Smith-and-Shannen-Doherty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kevin-Smith-and-Shannen-Doherty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kevin-Smith-and-Shannen-Doherty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位女演员本月早些时候去世，享年 53 岁</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/kevin-smith-remembers-shannen-dohertys-final-request-to-make-mallrats-2-3778924">凯文·史密斯 (Kevin Smith) 回忆起莎南·多尔蒂 (Shannen Doherty) 最后请求制作《Mallrats 2》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kevin-Smith-and-Shannen-Doherty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="凯文·史密斯和莎南·多尔蒂" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kevin-Smith-and-Shannen-Doherty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kevin-Smith-and-Shannen-Doherty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kevin-Smith-and-Shannen-Doherty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kevin-Smith-and-Shannen-Doherty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kevin-Smith-and-Shannen-Doherty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kevin-Smith-and-Shannen-Doherty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kevin-smith">凯文·史密斯</a>透露，莎南·多尔蒂最后提出了拍摄<em>《小老鼠 2》</em>的请求。</p><p>这位因出演<em>《魔咒》</em>和<em>《比佛利山庄 90210</em> 》而闻名的女演员在与乳腺癌抗争了 9 年之后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/charmed-actress-shannen-doherty-has-reportedly-died-aged-53-3774781">于本月早些时候去世，享年 53 岁</a>。</p><p>在她职业生涯的早期，她主演了史密斯 1995 年的邪典电影<em>《Mallrats》</em> ，导演在一次新的采访中透露，他与她的最后一次谈话集中在可能的续集上。</p><p> “我们最后一次谈话是关于她去泽西岛参加普通马拉松比赛，因为她做了很多坏事之类的事情，而且她遇到了<em>Mallrats 的</em>意外事件和其他事情，”他告诉<a href="https://people.com/kevin-smith-recalls-last-conversations-with-shannen-doherty-8684987" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《人物》杂志</em></a>。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="马尔鼠 |官方预告片| 1995年" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/toFqw3d7TlA?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “所以我当时想，‘天啊，莎南，你来我们的剧院看电影之类的，那只会让你登上王位。’”</p><p>史密斯回忆说，她“真的很想拍” <em>《Mallrats》的</em>续集，尽管史密斯在她去世后关门了，但制片人仍渴望“重新开始”。</p><p> “至少，作为‘为了 Shannen’，这是一件很酷的事情，”他建议道。</p><p>今年早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/shannen-doherty-mallrats-kevin-smith-killed-her-career-3568671">史密斯在多尔蒂</a>承认她的电影事业在<em>《Mallrats》</em>之后“死亡”后道歉。</p><p>至于续集，史密斯早在 2020 年就透露，他在封锁期间<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/kevin-smith-written-mallrats-2-script-during-quarantine-2654774">为后续电影《</a> <em>Mallrats 的暮光之城</em>》编写了剧本。 </p><figure id="attachment_3778948" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3778948" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3778948" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Shannen-Doherty-2024.jpg" alt="莎南·多尔蒂" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Shannen-Doherty-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Shannen-Doherty-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Shannen-Doherty-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Shannen-Doherty-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Shannen-Doherty-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Shannen-Doherty-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3778948" class="wp-caption-text">莎南·多尔蒂。图片来源：Getty/Gerardo Mora</figcaption></figure><p>多尔蒂的公关人员于七月初证实了她的去世，并在一份声明中表示：“我怀着沉重的心情确认女演员莎南·多尔蒂的去世。 7 月 13 日星期六，在与癌症抗争多年后，她最终失败了。</p><p> “这位忠诚的女儿、姐妹、阿姨和朋友周围都是她的亲人以及她的狗鲍伊。家人此时请求保护他们的隐私，以便他们能够平静地悲伤。”</p><p>消息传出后，证实多尔蒂在去世前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/shannen-doherty-recorded-five-charmed-rewatch-podcast-episodes-prior-to-death-3775303">录制了五集《<em>魅力》</em>重播播客《<em>哈利韦尔之家》</em></a> 。</p><p> “她对这个项目充满热情，并为扮演普鲁·哈利韦尔而感到自豪，我们希望这些剧集能为每个爱她的人带来一些安慰。普鲁，你的记忆依然存在，你的魔力依然存在。”播客在社交媒体上写道。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/kevin-smith-remembers-shannen-dohertys-final-request-to-make-mallrats-2-3778924">凯文·史密斯 (Kevin Smith) 回忆起莎南·多尔蒂 (Shannen Doherty) 最后请求制作《Mallrats 2》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
哥吉拉在 2024 年巴黎奥运会上代表“世界舞台上的整个金属界”感到压力https://www.nme.com/news/music/gojira-felt-Pressure-to-represent-the-whole-metal-community-on-the-world-stage-at-paris-2024-olympics-3778939？ utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=gojira 感受到了代表整个金属界参加 2024 年巴黎奥运会世界舞台的压力Max PilleyMon, 29 Jul 2024 15:48:09 +0000 Music NewsNewsMetal https://www.nme.com/?p=3778939 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/gojira_olympic-paris.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="哥吉拉" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/gojira_olympic-paris.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/gojira_olympic-paris-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/gojira_olympic-paris-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/gojira_olympic-paris-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/gojira_olympic-paris-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/gojira_olympic-paris-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他们成为第一支出现在奥运会开幕式上的金属乐队</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/gojira-felt-pressure-to-represent-the-whole-metal-community-on-the-world-stage-at-paris-2024-olympics-3778939">Gojira 感受到了在 2024 年巴黎奥运会上代表“整个金属界”的压力，</a>这一消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/gojira_olympic-paris.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="哥吉拉" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/gojira_olympic-paris.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/gojira_olympic-paris-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/gojira_olympic-paris-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/gojira_olympic-paris-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/gojira_olympic-paris-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/gojira_olympic-paris-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW201925078 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; color: #000000; font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Segoe UI Web', Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;"><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gojira">戈吉拉（Gojira）</a>表示，他们在2024年奥运会开幕式上露面期间承受着代表“整个金属社区”的压力。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/gojira-fortitude-review-2928116">Gojira  - “毅力”评论：地震金属抹布，将重岩推向前进</a></strong></li></ul><p>法国重金属制品<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-gojira-perform-ah-ca-ira-in-the-paris-olympics-opening-ceremony-3778455">在周五（7月26日）在巴黎举行的典礼上与实验性歌剧歌手玛丽娜·维奥蒂（Marina Viotti）一起进行了爆炸性的表演</a>。</p><p>这首歌翻译为“它会很好”，在法国大革命中被普及，并被包括在仪式的“自由”部分中，该部分重点是法国的政治行动和自由历史。</p><p>乐队出现在城堡的侧面，周围是火，红色彩带爆发来代表血液。他们成为历史上第一个在奥运会开幕式上演出的金属乐队。他们的表演是在致力于<em>情人苦难的</em>一部分之后的，并在斩首玛丽·安托瓦内特（Marie Antoinette）唱歌之后。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="in" dir="ltr"> Gojira <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/paris2024?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">＃Paris2024</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/ceremoniedouverture?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#ceremoniedouverture</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/OpeningCeremony?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#openingcereymen</a> <a href="https://t.co/9TYBMMjiCE">pic.twitter.com/9tybmmjice</a></p><p> - 约翰（@Johjohbat） <a href="https://twitter.com/johjohbat/status/1816901900345692394?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024年7月26日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>现在，乐队的主持人乔·杜普兰蒂尔（Joe Duplantier）在与<em><a href="https://www.nytimes.com/article/opening-ceremony-heavy-metal-band-gojira.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《纽约时报》（New York Times）</a></em>交谈时解释说，表演使乐队在世界上最大的电视观众之一面前感到压力代表该类型及其追随者。</p><p> Duplantier说，他希望表演成为“世界舞台上的整个金属社区”的自豪感，并补充说，鉴于其与革命时期的联系，这首歌特别合适。</p><p>他说：“这是法国历史上非常血腥的时代。” “所以这是非常金属的。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C95oFxrAd_q/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 5